text: André le Goupil (born 7 January 1931) is a French equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Manche
